[thinking] **Exploring dynamic proxies**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m thinking about using dynamic proxies for Runnable. It seems like native support might be there, and I wonder if Proxy.newProxyInstance needs specific metadata at runtime. But perhaps any generated metadata would be external. I should also consider if JDK proxy can be useful in this case. Overall, it looks like I need to simplify the file and eliminate any helpers to make things more straightforward.
